name: EditingState
shortdesc: The editing state of the file in Version Cue.

property.name: EDITING_UNKNOWN
property.shortdesc: The editing status is not known.

property.name: EDITING_NOWHERE
property.shortdesc: The file is not currently in use and is not locked.

property.name: EDITING_LOCALLY
property.shortdesc: The file has been modified locally and not locked.

property.name: EDITING_LOCALLY_LOCKED
property.shortdesc: The file has been locked locally and may be modified.

property.name: EDITING_CONFLICT
property.shortdesc: The file was modified locally or remotely while it was locked and therefore two versions exist.
